oport: It's your chance to learn more about the world of technology Blockchain and participate in club projects!
description: We are university students from the Inteli Technology College - Instituto of Technology and Leadership. We created the Inteli Blockchain with the objective of promoting the use of this technology and solving problems real.
projectDescription1: Have you ever wondered what it would be like to have your entire student curriculum on a blockchain? This was the project carried out in partnership with Inteli
projectDescription2: Making donations to another country seems kind of doable...right? Wrong! With Our Neighbors, a project developed in the Ethereum SP hackathon, this has become easier and more practical.
